# TrafficSignWebService

API: http://localhost:5000/api/v1/trafficsign <br>
Method: POST <br>
Body: <br>
```
{'img': <string img base 64> }
```
Respond: <br>
```
{
  'img': <string img base 64>,
  'info': [
    {
      "Des": <string mô tả img>,
      "img": <string img base 64 icon trafficsign>,
      "sign": <name sign>
    }
  ]
}
```

{

}
